@section Signing In

You'll sign in to Tootsville using your Google account.

If you're already logged in to Google when you visit the site, you'll just
be asked to authorize Tootsville once.

If you aren't yet signed in to your Google account, you'll have the
opportunity to do so.

Once you've signed in, you'll go directly to your Toot character.

